				<p>This mobile page is built in Ruby on Rails with templates generated by jQTouch. The page is hosted via Heroku and the code is available in a public GitHub repository <%= link_to "here", "http://github.com/FangedParakeet/SMerchPro", rel: "external", target: "blank" %>.</p>
