				</div>
				<div class="scroll">
					<h2><strong>"I live at the foot of my heights: how high are my peaks? No one has told me yet. But I know my valleys well."</strong>
					--Friedrich Nietzsche</h2>
					<ul class="rounded">
						<li><p>I am a coder, a musician, a University of Chicago alumnus, and above all a builder. With two years of coding experience, an economics degree, and a lot of determination I am venturing into the wilderness, hunting for professional experience to continue my development. I see myself as more of a back-end developer, in that I love getting stuck into code and controllers, my eyes lighting up when I see unconstructed model relationships. However, as any developer knows, it's impossible not to let one get many fingers stuck into many pies, so I have over time developed strong front-end skills as well, becoming well-versed in anything from CSS through AJAX. I had to do everything here after all...</p>
						</li>
						<li style="text-align:center"><%= image_tag 'sort of me.png', width: '320' %></li>
						<li><p>Essentially I have a passion for learning, facing down challenges, and above all building beautiful, clean, and meaningful code. I want to learn more skills so that I can build solutions to solve big problems. If you think these are qualities that you relish in a programmer, please get in touch with me!</p>
						</li>
